  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy Study of HGP1207 in Patients With Pulmonary Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase III Study to Evaluate Efficacy and Safety of HGP1207 in Patients With Pulmonary Hypertension Associated With Systolic Heart Failure</official_title>
